data.enText: the parts of a town or city that are furthest from the centre
They live on the outskirts of Milan.

simple_means.memory_skill: out 出，外 + skirts 位于…的边缘 → 城市周边 → 郊区

tr: outlying areas (as of a city or town)
example: they lived on the outskirts of Houston
they mingled in the outskirts of the crowd

value.def: The outskirts of a city or town are the parts of it that are farthest away from its centre.

example.ex: Hours later we reached the outskirts of New York.
example.tran: 我们几小时后到达了纽约市郊。
